__NOTOC__ bool '''CanRaiseActor''' (int ''tid'');
==Usage== Checks to see if the actor or actors with the specified {{c|[[TID|tid]]}} are viable for resurrection. If {{c|tid}} is 0, the check is done on the activator of the script.
===Parameters=== *''tid'': the {{c|tid}} of the actor or actors to check.
===Return Value=== The function returns {{c|true}} if the actor can be resurrected, otherwise it returns {{c|false}}. In case multiple actors are checked, the function only returns {{c|true}} if all of the actors can be resurrected. If at least one of them fails the check, the returned value is {{c|false}}.
